<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="light" lang="it">
<head>
  <%- include('../partials/head') %>
</head>
<body class="bg-background-light dark:bg-background-dark font-display">
<div class="relative flex min-h-screen w-full flex-col">
<div class="flex-grow w-full">
<div class="min-h-screen grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2">
<!-- Left Column: Login Form -->
<div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center p-8 sm:p-12 bg-white dark:bg-background-dark">
<div class="w-full max-w-md">
<!-- Logo -->
<div class="mb-8 text-center lg:text-left">
<div class="flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start gap-3">
<img src="/images/logo.png" alt="SmileAgent Logo" class="w-12 h-12 object-contain">
<span class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">SmileAgent</span>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Heading -->
<div class="mb-8 text-center lg:text-left">
<p class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-4xl font-black leading-tight tracking-[-0.033em]">Bentornato!</p>
<p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 text-base font-normal leading-normal mt-3">L'automazione intelligente per il tuo studio dentistico</p>
</div>

<% if (error === 'credentials') { %>
<div class="mb-4 p-4 bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900/30 border border-red-400 dark:border-red-700 text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 rounded-lg">
Email o password non corretti.
</div>
<% } else if (error === 'server') { %>
<div class="mb-4 p-4 bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900/30 border border-red-400 dark:border-red-700 text-red-700 dark:text-red-400 rounded-lg">
Errore del server. Riprova pi√π tardi.
</div>
<% } %>

<!-- Form -->
<form action="/login" method="POST" class="flex flex-col gap-6">
<!-- Email Field -->
<label class="flex flex-col w-full">
<p class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200 text-base font-medium leading-normal pb-2">Indirizzo Email</p>
<div class="relative flex w-full flex-1 items-stretch">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-gray-600">mail</span>
<input name="email" class="form-input flex w-full min-w-0 flex-1 resize-none overflow-hidden rounded-lg text-gray-900 dark:text-white focus:outline-0 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/50 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 h-14 placeholder:text-gray-600 pl-12 pr-4 py-[15px] text-base font-normal leading-normal" placeholder="studio@esempio.it" type="email" value="studio@dentalrossi.it" required/>
</div>
</label>
<!-- Password Field -->
<label class="flex flex-col w-full">
<p class="text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-200 text-base font-medium leading-normal pb-2">Password</p>
<div class="relative flex w-full flex-1 items-stretch">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined absolute left-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-gray-600">lock</span>
<input name="password" class="form-input flex w-full min-w-0 flex-1 resize-none overflow-hidden rounded-lg text-gray-900 dark:text-white focus:outline-0 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-primary/50 border border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-700 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 h-14 placeholder:text-gray-600 pl-12 pr-4 py-[15px] text-base font-normal leading-normal" placeholder="Inserisci la tua password" type="password" value="demo123" required/>
</div>
</label>
<!-- Submit Button -->
<button type="submit" class="flex items-center justify-center text-center font-medium relative rounded-lg px-6 py-4 text-base bg-primary text-white hover:bg-primary/90 w-full h-14">
Accedi
</button>
<!-- Demo credentials -->
<div class="text-center text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 bg-blue-50 dark:bg-blue-900/20 p-3 rounded-lg">
<p class="font-semibold mb-1">Credenziali Demo:</p>
<p>Email: <span class="font-mono">studio@dentalrossi.it</span></p>
<p>Password: <span class="font-mono">demo123</span></p>
</div>
</form>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Right Column: Branding -->
<div class="hidden lg:flex flex-col justify-center items-center p-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-purple-500/20">
<div class="text-center max-w-md">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary" style="font-size: 120px; font-variation-settings: 'FILL' 1;">
dentistry
</span>
<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8 mb-4">
Gestione Studio Semplificata
</h2>
<p class="text-lg text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
Risparmia ore ogni settimana con l'automazione AI per il tuo studio dentistico.
</p>
<div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
<div>
<p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">500+</p>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Studi attivi</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">95%</p>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Soddisfazione</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">20h</p>
<p class="text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">Risparmiate/mese</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
